misconceptions.remediation_hint:
Change the grading logic to an if–else-if–else chain, such as:
if (grade >= 90) {...}
else if (grade >= 80) {...}
else if (grade >= 70) {...}
else if (grade >= 60) {...}
else {...}
Alternatively, include both lower and upper bounds in each condition so that the ranges do not overlap.

